OL,3,C'Climate Whiplash' puts world's
OL,4,Cbiggest cities at risk of drought and
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FThe increase in weather-related
OL,8,Fdisasters has been linked to man-made
OL,9,Fclimate change, as ITV News' Science
OL,10,FCorrespondent explains
OL,12,FMany of the world's most populous
OL,13,Fcities are increasingly seeing their
OL,14,Fweather flip flop from extreme drought
OL,15,Fto heavy rainfall - a phenomenon that
OL,16,Fhas been dubbed 'climate whiplash' by
OL,17,Fthe charity WaterAid.
