OL,3,C'Climate Whiplash' puts world's
OL,4,Cbiggest cities at risk of drought and
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FFor the first time, a new report by
OL,8,Fthe charity gives us a worldwide, city
OL,9,Fby city breakdown of how our changing
OL,10,Fclimate is affecting water.
OL,12,FToo much water and you get flooding,
OL,13,Ftoo little and you have drought.
OL,15,FThe report, produced with the help of
OL,16,FThe University of Bristol and Cardiff
OL,17,FUniversity, found weather-related
OL,18,Fdisasters have increased 400% in the
OL,19,Flast 50 years. The increase has been
OL,20,Flinked to man-made climate change.
