OL,3,C'Climate Whiplash' puts world's
OL,4,Cbiggest cities at risk of drought and
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FHere are 112 of the world's biggest
OL,8,Fcities. The darker the red, the faster
OL,9,Fthey're drying. The darker the blue,
OL,10,Fthe wetter they're getting.
OL,12,FAll of Europe's biggest cities are
OL,13,Fbecoming more prone to drought.
OL,15,FSouthern Asian cities are at an
OL,16,Fincreasing risk of floods.
