OL,3,C'Climate Whiplash' puts world's
OL,4,Cbiggest cities at risk of drought and
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,F"This research comes at a pivotal
OL,8,Ftime, as we're seeing a sweep of
OL,9,Fglobal aid cuts, which could leave
OL,10,Fbasic human rights hanging in the
OL,11,Fbalance," said Tim Wainwright,
OL,12,FWaterAid UK's Chief Executive.
OL,14,F"(It) highlights the devastating
OL,15,Fshifts in extreme climate patterns
OL,16,Facross all continents, with the impact
OL,17,Ffelt most clearly on low-income
OL,18,Fcountries, where the absence of water
OL,19,Fbecomes not just a challenge, but a
OL,20,Fmatter of life and death."
