OL,3,C'Climate Whiplash' puts world's
OL,4,Cbiggest cities at risk of drought and
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FThe other measure is vulnerability -
OL,8,Fhow geared up cities are to cope?
OL,9,FMadrid, Barcelona and Paris all score
OL,10,Fworse than cities in Australia and
OL,11,FAmerica, because of their aging
OL,12,Finfrastructure.
OL,14,FAnd it's a similar story in London -
OL,15,Fthe only UK city analysed. Whilst the
OL,16,Flevel of drying is quite mild, our
OL,17,Fwater defences and storage aren't
OL,18,Fgreat. A small example, but we haven't
OL,19,Fopened a single new reservoir in the
OL,20,Fpast 30 years.
